    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/5f06b27eaef8a0cbe23fb73f8ee70651.poster.avif?t=1758063240\" aria-label=\"The Game&#039;s Logo with &quot;Pip Pepper Park Planner&quot; in bold black and white letters, in front of a blue chequered animated background.\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/5f06b27eaef8a0cbe23fb73f8ee70651.webm?t=1758063240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A GAME TO REFLECT ON THE SPACES WE SHARE‎ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pip Pepper Park Planner</strong> is an <i>upcoming </i> <i>cozy</i> + <i>thinky</i> game in which you play as <strong>Pip</strong>, a <i>little </i>bird with a <i>big </i>job: to design parks for animals to enjoy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different habitats, discover the needs of diverse animals and fully customize your parks. <i>Can you build a park that all the animals will love?‎ </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/e0d2e6d23ea96f25ecb8db711358f465.poster.avif?t=1758063240\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/e0d2e6d23ea96f25ecb8db711358f465.webm?t=1758063240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOUR CHOICES HAVE AN IMPACT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/a6f1c49beb551937fcba775c284b588f.poster.avif?t=1758063240\" aria-label=\"A two-sections banner. The section to the left contains the word &quot;CREATE&quot; in bold black and white letters in a chequered moving blue background. The Section to the right contains gameplay footage of the Game&#039;s Demo, showcasing a park customization sequence.\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/a6f1c49beb551937fcba775c284b588f.webm?t=1758063240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create</strong> your own fully customizable parks. With many possible combinations, you decide what happens next.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/50277cf562f2de6c73a92fd919eae868.poster.avif?t=1758063240\" aria-label=\"A two-sections banner. The section to the left contains the word &quot;INTERACT&quot; in bold black and white letters in a chequered moving blue background. The Section to the right contains gameplay footage of the Game&#039;s Demo, showcasing dialogue sequences and interaction with objects in the game world.\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/50277cf562f2de6c73a92fd919eae868.webm?t=1758063240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interact</strong> with a variety of quirky animal characters. Learn about their unique needs and interests through fun dialogue interactions.<br> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/d4d7ab7bafc3b68f95972635f4422188.poster.avif?t=1758063240\" aria-label=\"A two-sections banner. The section to the left contains the word &quot;INTERACT&quot; in bold black and white letters in a chequered moving blue background. The Section to the right contains gameplay footage of the Game&#039;s Demo, showcasing the Player platforming freely, jumping on top of structures of the level in the game world.\" width=1170 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204530/extras/d4d7ab7bafc3b68f95972635f4422188.webm?t=1758063240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore</strong> a playground of possibilities where your choices matter. Replayable levels for different outcomes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
